Ms%20Twitchen's%20favour%2C%20finding%20First%20Grade%20Projects%20liable%20for%20unfair%20dismissal%20and%20awarding%20her%2028%2C000%20pounds%20in%20compensation.%C2%A0Judge%20Robin%20Harvard%20pointed%20out%20a%20significant%20inconsistency%20in%20Jeremy%20Morgan's%20reasoning%20for%20making%20her%20redundant.%20During%20their%20February%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Morgan%20had%20claimed%20the%20business%20was%20doing%20well%20and%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20financial%20difficulties.%20He%20also%20didn't%20mention%20the%20new%20software%20that%20supposedly%20made%20Ms%20Twitchen's%20role%20obsolete%2C%20even%20during%20their%20April%20phone%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20criticised%20First%20Grade's%20failure%20to%20''produce%20any%20evidence%20of%20the%20alleged%20financial%20difficulties%20or%20the%20new%20software''%20during%20the%20court%20case.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20at%20no%20stage%20did%20Ms%20Twitchen%20receive%20a%20written%20statement%20setting%20out%20the%20reasons%20for%20her%20dismissal.%C2%A0Judge%20Havard%20ruled%20that%20Ms%20Twitchen%20was%20dismissed%20because%20she%20was%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20her%20dismissal%20was%20%26quot%3Bunfair%2C%20discriminatory%2C%20and%20caused%20significant%20emotional%20distress.%26quot%3B%20He%20emphasised%20that%20being%20fired%20while%20pregnant%20and%20losing%20financial%20stability%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20her%2C%20particularly%20given%20her%20family%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20Grade%20Projects%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walesonline.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fwales-news%2Fboss-laid-member-staff-because-30174272%5C%22%3EWalesOnline%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20extremely%20disappointed%20with%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20tribunal.%20We%20are%20actively%20reviewing%20all%20relevant%20information%20and%20considering%20all%20available%20o