%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fg7-defence-ministers-concerned-by-attacks-on-peacekeepers-vow-kyiv-support%2Famp_articleshow%2F114388158.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fg7-defence-ministers-concerned-by-attacks-on-peacekeepers-vow-kyiv-support%2Famp_articleshow%2F114388158.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Kajol%20opened%20up%20on%20her%20parents'%20separation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729393192000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114388094%2Cimgsize-78389.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-when-kajol-opened-up-on-her-parents-separation-when-she-was-barely-5-it-could-have-gone-very-wrong-%2Farticleshow%2F114388028.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114388028.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20separated%20when%20I%20was%20about%20four-and-a-half%20years%20old%2C%20and%20it%20could%20have%20gone%20very%20wrong.%20I%20have%20so%20many%20friends%20whose%20parents%20are%20together%20till%20today%20but%20not%20in%20the%20best%20spaces.%20They%20have%20not%20had%20great%20childhoods.%20I%20loved%20my%20father%20separately%2C%20I%20loved%20my%20mother%20separately%2C%20and%20I%20loved%20them%20together%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-when-kajol-opened-up-on-her-parents-separation-when-she-was-barely-5-it-could-have-gone-very-wrong-%2Farticleshow%2F114388028.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2235%25%20Pay%20Raise%2C%20%247%2C000%20Signing%20Bonus%3A%20Boeing's%20Deal%20With%20Protesting%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBoeing%20and%20its%20striking%20Seattle-area%20workers%20have%20reached%20a%20tentative%20deal%20to%20end%20a%20more%20than%20month-long%20stoppage%2C%20the%20union%20said%20Saturday.%20Boeing%20confirmed%20a%20tentative%20deal%20was%20reached%20and%20said%20it%20includes%20a%2035%20percent%20pay%20raise%20over%20four%20years%20and%20a%20one-time%20signing%20bonus%20of%20%247%2C000.%20Union%20members%20will%20vote%20Wednesday%20on%20the%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20began%20September%2013%20in%20a%20dispute%20over%20pay%20and%20other%20compensation%20issues%2C%20the%20International%20Association%20of%20Machinists%20and%20Aerospace%20Workers%20said%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20in%20a%20message%20to%20its%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20warrants%20presenting%20to%20the%20members%20and%20is%20worthy%20of%20your%20consideration%2C%26quot%3B%20IAM%20Union%20District%20751%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20by%20some%2033%2C000%20unionized%20workers%2C%20mainly%20in%20Washington%20state%2C%20halted%20work%20at%20two%20Seattle-area%20assembly%20plants%20and%20production%20of%20its%20737%20MAX%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20were%20seeking%20hefty%20wage%20hikes%20and%20other%20gains%2C%20complaining%20of%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20of%20near-flat%20wages%20amid%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWage%20increases%20had%20been%20a%20stumbling%20block.%20Boeing%20first%20offered%20a%2025%20percent%20raise%2C%20and%20then%2030%20percent%2C%20while%20the%20union%20wanted%2040%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20had%20also%20been%20pressing%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20a%20traditional%20employer-paid%20pension%20plan%2C%20which%20Boeing%20withdrew%20in%202014%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20get%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20retirement%20plans%20had%20been%20a%20staple%20of%20the%20American%20workplace%20for%20decades%20but%20they%20are%20now%20rare%2C%20as%20the%20onus%20for%20preparing%20for%20old%20age%20has%20shifted%20from%20employer%20to%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20among%20the%20sweeteners%20Boeing%20is%20now%20offering%20are%20enhanced%20contributions%20to%20largely%20worker-funded%20retirement%20schemes%20called%20401(k)%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20has%20cost%20an%20estimated%20%247.6%20billion%20in%20direct%20losses%20--%20including%20at%20least%20%244.35%20billion%20for%20Boeing%20and%20almost%20%242%20billion%20for%20its%20suppliers%20--%20the%20Anderson%20Economic%20Group%20consultancy%20said%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20said%20in%20a%20one-sentence%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20look%20forward%20to%20our%20employees%20voting%20on%20the%20negotiated%20proposal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20stoppage%20added%20to%20the%20company's%20litany%20of%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20sank%20into%20further%20turmoil%20in%20January%20when%20a%20window%20panel%20blew%20out%20mid-flight%20on%20an%20Alaska%20Airlines%20plane%2C%20necessitating%20an%20emergency%20landing%20on%20a%20737%20MAX%2C%20the%20aircraft%20involved%20in%20two%20fatal%20crashes%20in%202018%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20led%20to%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20tightening%20oversight%20of%20Boeing's%20production%20processes%2C%20capping%20the%20company's%20output.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week%20Boeing%20unveiled%20measures%20meant%20to%20replenish%20its%20cash%20flow%2C%20including%20an%20intention%20to%20raise%20up%20to%20%2425%20billion%2C%20as%20it%20navigated%20recurrent%20production%20problems%20and%20the%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Boeing%20said%20it%20planned%20to%20cut%2010%20percent%20of%20its%20workforce%20as%20it%20projected%20a%20large%20third-quarter%20loss%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20labor%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cuts%20of%2017%2C000%20positions%20globally%20will%20include%20executives%2C%20managers%20and%20employees%2C%20according%20to%20Chief%20Executive%20Kelly%20Ortberg%2C%20who%20added%20that%20the%20company%20must%20%26quot%3Breset%20our%20workforce%20levels%20to%20align%20with%20our%20financial%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20fallout%20from%20the%20strike%2C%20Boeing%20has%20said%20it%20is%20pushing%20back%20first%20delivery%20of%20its%20777X%20plane%20to%202026%20from%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20much-delayed%20jet%20was%20originally%20supposed%20to%20enter%20service%20in%20January%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729392720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F176cls7o_boeing_625x300_20_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F35-pay-raise-7-000-signing-bonus-boeings-deal-with-protesting-workers-6829618%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boeing%20workers%20began%20a%20strike%20on%20September%2013%20in%20a%20dispute%20over%20pay%20and%20other%20compensation%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F35-pay-raise-7-000-signing-bonus-boeings-deal-with-protesting-workers-6829618%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kejriwal%20holds%20marathon%20AAP%20meet%2C%20urges%20workers%20to%20win%20all%20seats%20in%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729392515000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fkejriwal-holds-marathon-aap-meet-urges-workers-to-try-to-win-all-70-seats-124102000033_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Claiming%20that%20no%20party%20in%20India's%20history%20has%20been%20harassed%20as%20much%20as%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20former%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Ar