20title%20clash%20of%20the%20tournament%20from%20Lahore%20even%20if%20the%20arch-rivals%20qualify%20for%20the%20final%20on%20March%209%2C%20sources%20said%20on%20Friday.%20The%20PCB's%20stance%20on%20hosting%20the%20final%20is%20up%20for%20debate%20when%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20Board%20members%20meet%20in%20Dubai%20from%20October%2018%20to%2021.%20%26quot%3BThe%20PCB's%20first%20choice%20and%20priority%20is%20to%20host%20entire%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20they%20are%20counting%20on%20this%20but%20internally%20the%20Board%20is%20also%20mentally%20prepared%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20Indian%20government%20not%20allowing%20its%20team%20to%20play%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20India's%20matches%20being%20held%20in%20UAE%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20PCB%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20PCB%20has%20decided%20even%20in%20the%20event%20of%20India%20not%20playing%20in%20Pakistan%20they%20want%20the%20final%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Lahore.%20Even%20if%20India%20qualifies%20for%20the%20final%20the%20PCB%20wants%20the%20ICC%20to%20hold%20the%20match%20at%20the%20Gaddafi%20stadium%20in%20Lahore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bilateral%20cricketing%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20freezed%20since%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20in%20which%20175%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20close%20to%20300%20suffered%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20may%20request%20the%20ICC%20to%20hold%20the%20tournament%20in%20a%20hybrid%20model%20and%20relocate%20their%20matches%20to%20either%20Sri%20Lanka%20or%20Dubai%2C%20like%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaddafi%20hosted%20the%20final%20of%20the%201996%20World%20Cup.%20The%20seating%20capacity%20at%20the%20stadium%20is%20being%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20claimed%20that%20PCB%20Chairman%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20and%20Chief%20Operating%20Officer%20Salman%20Naseer%20will%20be%20submitting%20details%20of%20the%20costs%20the%20PCB%20is%20bearing%20to%20renovate%20and%20upgrade%20the%20stadiums%20in%20Karachi%2C%20Rawalpindi%20and%20Lahore%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20will%20submit%20the%20details%20including%20the%20highest%20budget%20of%20around%207%20billion%20earmarked%20for%20renovation%20work%20at%20the%20stadium%20in%20Lahore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Naqvi%20will%20make%20it%20clear%20at%20the%20ICC%20meeting%20that%20even%20if%20India%20can't%20come%20for%20the%20entire%20tournament%20to%20Pakistan%20they%20must%20play%20the%20final%20in%20Lahore%20if%20they%20qualify.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20this%20talk%20that%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20might%20be%20altogether%20moved%20to%20another%20location%20has%20also%20bothered%20the%20PCB%20and%20they%20will%20discuss%20this%20as%20Naqvi%20is%20adamant%20that%20Pakistan%20will%20host%20the%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20England%20and%20Wales%20Cricket%20Board%20(ECB)%20senior%20officials%20ruffled%20feathers%20in%20the%20PCB%20with%20a%20statement%20this%20week%20that%20moving%20the%20tournament%20out%20of%20Pakistan%20was%20an%20option%20available%20to%20the%20ICC%20and%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20said%20that%20the%20PCB%20is%20expecting%20to%20get%20some%20sort%20of%20viable%20answer%20from%20the%20BCCI%20officials%20at%20the%20coming%20meeting%20on%20the%20progress%20they%20have%20made%20(if%20any)%20on%20seeking%20clearance%20from%20their%20government%20to%20send%20their%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20early%20next%20year%20for%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPCB%20officials%20will%20present%20detailed%20updates%20on%20the%20preparations%20for%20the%20tournament%20and%20the%20progress%20made%20on%20construction%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20has%20been%20placed%20in%20Group%20A%20alongside%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20and%20the%20PCB%20has%20proposed%20holding%20all%20of%20India's%20games%20in%20Lahore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELahore%20is%20set%20to%20host%20seven%20matches%2C%20including%20the%20final.%20Karachi%20will%20stage%20the%20opening%20match%20and%20a%20semi-final%2C%20while%20Rawalpindi%20will%20host%20five%20matches%2C%20including%20the%20other%20semi-final.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729390200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fh11amgco_india-pakistan-afp_625x300_08_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-mentally-prepared-for-indias-champions-trophy-2025-refusal-report-says-6820071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20is%20mentally%20prepared%20for%20India's%20refusal%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20country%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20but%20it%20won't%20move%20the%20title%20clash%20of%20the%20tournament%20from%20Lahore%20even%20if%20the%20arch-rivals%20qualify%20for%20the%20final%20on%20March%209.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-mentally-prepared-for-indias-champions-trophy-2025-refusal-report-says-6820071%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%3A%20President%20Xi%20directs%20PLA%20rocket%20force%20to%20strengthen%20deterrence%20and%20combat%20capabilities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729389846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114387688%2Cimgsize-688319.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-president-xi-directs-pla-rocket-force-to-strengthen-deterrence-and-combat-capabilities%2Farticleshow%2F114387603.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114