s-lives-vs-bollywood-wives-s3-riddhima-kapoor-sahni-says-when-rishi-kapoor-passed-away-the-family-never-showed-emotions-to-each-other-%2Farticleshow%2F114387515.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114387515.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EComing%20back%20to%20the%20show%2C%20for%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20her%20in%20the%20very%20first%20episode%20of%20the%20series%2C%20the%20makers%20thought%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20her%20brother%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%2C%20who%20gave%20an%20unfiltered%20introduction%20of%20Riddhima.%20His%20video%20was%20played%20in%20the%20episode%2C%20which%20began%20with%20Ranbir%20first%20being%20confused%20about%20the%20right%20title%2C%20and%20then%20the%20season%2C%20wondering%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20already%20the%20third%20installment%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffabulous-lives-vs-bollywood-wives-s3-riddhima-kapoor-sahni-says-when-rishi-kapoor-passed-away-the-family-never-showed-emotions-to-each-other-%2Farticleshow%2F114387515.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Classified%20US%20Intelligence%20Leaked%2C%20Documents%20Show%20Israel's%20Plans%20For%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20highly%20classified%20US%20intelligence%20documents%20have%20leaked%2C%20allegedly%20exposing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hits-beirut-gaza-after-assassination-attempt-on-benjamin-netanyahu-by-iran-backed-hezbollah-6829326%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll_Imagetopscroll%5C%22%3EIsrael%3C%2Fa%3E's%20military%20preparations%20for%20a%20potential%20strike%20on%20Iran%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F10%2F19%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fus-intelligence-israel-iran.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20documents%2C%20originating%20from%20the%20National%20Geospatial-Intelligence%20Agency%20(NGA)%20-%20%26quot%3Bresponsible%20for%20analysing%20images%20and%20information%20collected%20by%20American%20spy%20satellites%26quot%3B%20-%20offer%20insights%20into%20Israeli%20military%20exercises%20and%20operational%20readiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20documents%2C%20dated%20October%2015%20and%2016%2C%20were%20circulated%20on%20Telegram%20by%20accounts%20largely%20associated%20with%20pro-Iran%20sentiments.%20They%20provide%20detailed%20analyses%20of%20satellite%20images%20showing%20Israel's%20military%20exercises%2C%20which%20appear%20to%20be%20in%20preparation%20for%20a%20retaliatory%20strike%20on%20Iran.%20The%20potential%20strike%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20escalating%20tensions%20following%20an%20Iranian%20missile%20barrage%20on%20October%201%2C%20itself%20a%20retaliation%20for%20an%20earlier%20Israeli%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnetanyahu-says-attempt-by-irans-proxy-hezbollah-to-assassinate-me-and-my-wife-was-a-grave-mistake-6827757%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BGrave%20Mistake%26quot%3B%3A%20Netanyahu%20On%20Hezbollah's%20%26quot%3BAssassination%26quot%3B%20Attempt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20documents%20is%20titled%20%26quot%3BIsrael%3A%20Air%20Force%20Continues%20Preparations%20for%20Strike%20on%20Iran%26quot%3B%20and%20outlines%20recent%20Israeli%20exercises%20that%20seem%20to%20rehearse%20a%20potential%20military%20operation%20against%20Iran.%20These%20preparations%20reportedly%20include%20air-to-air%20refuelling%20operations%2C%20search-and-rescue%20missions%2C%20and%20the%20repositioning%20of%20missile%20systems%20in%20anticipation%20of%20potential%20Iranian%20strikes.%20The%20second%20document%20reveals%20Israeli%20efforts%20to%20move%20munitions%20and%20other%20military%20assets%20to%20strategic%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20documents%20describe%20Israeli%20military%20movements%20and%20exercises%2C%20they%20do%20not%20provide%20satellite%20images%20themselves.%20The%20US%20intelligence%20gathered%20from%20these%20images%20suggests%20that%20Israel%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20a%20strike%2C%20but%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20these%20documents%20reveal%20the%20full%20scope%20of%20Israel's%20plans%20for%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20Response%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaks%20have%20reportedly%20prompted%20immediate%20concern%20within%20the%20US%20government.%20US%20officials%20are%20divided%20over%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20leak%2C%20with%20some%20downplaying%20its%20impact%20given%20that%20the%20documents%20do%20not%20reveal%20new%20American%20capabilities.%20Others%2C%20however%2C%20are%20alarmed%20by%20the%20exposure%20of%20Israel's%20sensitive%20military%20plans%2C%20particularly%20at%20a%20time%20of%20heightened%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20when%20asked%20during%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20Germany%20whether%20he%20was%20aware%20of%20Israel's%20planned%20strike%20on%20Iran%20and%20its%20targets%2C%20responded%20with%20a%20brief%20%26quot%3BYes%20and%20yes%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20declined%20to%20elaborate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20exact%20source%20of%20the%20leak%20remains%20unknown%2C%20early%20indications%20suggest%20that%20the%20documents%20may%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20a%20lower-level%20US%20government%20employee.%20A%20joint%20investigation%20by%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20U.S.%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20and%20the%20FBI%20is%20underway%20to%20determine%20how%20the%20information%20was%20leaked%20and%20whether%20more%20documents%20could%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729389000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2pt0puu_israel-arm