C%20echoing%20language%20used%20by%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20came%20as%20Israeli%20military%20strikes%20killed%20at%20least%2035%20people%20across%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20its%20forces%20tightened%20a%20siege%20around%20hospitals%20in%20Jabalia%20in%20the%20north%20of%20the%20enclave%2C%20Palestinian%20health%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20drops%20the%20weapon%20and%20hands%20over%20the%20hostages%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20leave%20and%20live%20in%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20leaflet%2C%20written%20in%20Arabic%2C%20read%2C%20according%20to%20residents%20of%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Khan%20Younis%20and%20images%20circulating%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaflet's%20wording%20was%20from%20a%20statement%20by%20Netanyahu%20on%20Thursday%20after%20Sinwar%20was%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20soldiers%20operating%20in%20Rafah%2C%20in%20the%20south%20near%20the%20Egyptian%20border%2C%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20October%207%20attack%20Sinwar%20planned%20on%20Israeli%20communities%20a%20year%20ago%20killed%20around%201%2C200%20people%2C%20with%20another%20253%20dragged%20back%20to%20Gaza%20as%20hostages%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20tallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20subsequent%20war%20has%20devastated%20Gaza%2C%20killing%20more%20than%2042%2C500%20Palestinians%2C%20with%20another%2010%2C000%20uncounted%20dead%20thought%20to%20lie%20under%20the%20rubble%2C%20Gaza%20health%20authorities%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20central%20Gaza%20Strip%20camp%20of%20Al-Maghzai%2C%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20a%20house%20killed%2011%20people%2C%20while%20another%20strike%20at%20the%20nearby%20camp%20of%20Nuseirat%20killed%20four%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20other%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20two%20separate%20strikes%20in%20the%20south%20Gaza%20cities%20of%20Khan%20Younis%20and%20Rafah%2C%20medics%20said%2C%20while%20seven%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Shati%20camp%20in%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%20Saturday%2C%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20killed%20three%20Palestinians%20in%20Nuseirat%20in%20central%20Gaza%2C%20medics%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20on%20Friday%2C%20medics%20said%2033%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20were%20killed%20and%2085%20others%20were%20wounded%20in%20Israeli%20strikes%20that%20destroyed%20at%20least%20three%20houses%20in%20Jabalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20it%20was%20unaware%20of%20that%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20forces%20were%20continuing%20operations%20against%20Hamas%20across%20the%20enclave%2C%20killing%20several%20gunmen%20in%20Rafah%20and%20Jabalia%20and%20dismantling%20military%20infrastructure.%20Palestinian%20medics%20said%20five%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20Jabalia%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEVACUATION%20ORDERS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20and%20medics%20said%20Israeli%20forces%20had%20tightened%20their%20siege%20on%20Jabalia%2C%20the%20largest%20of%20the%20enclave's%20eight%20historic%20camps%2C%20which%20it%20encircled%20by%20also%20sending%20tanks%20to%20nearby%20towns%20of%20Beit%20Hanoun%20and%20Beit%20Lahiya%20and%20issuing%20evacuation%20orders%20to%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20said%20evacuation%20orders%20were%20aimed%20at%20separating%20Hamas%20fighters%20from%20civilians%20and%20denied%20that%20there%20was%20any%20systematic%20plan%20to%20clear%20civilians%20out%20of%20Jabalia%20or%20other%20northern%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jabalia%2C%20residents%20said%20Israeli%20army%20forces%20besieged%20several%20shelters%20housing%20displaced%20families%20before%20they%20stormed%20them%20and%20detained%20dozens%20of%20men.%20Footage%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%2C%20which%20Reuters%20could%20not%20immediately%20verify%2C%20showed%20dozens%20of%20Palestinian%20men%20sitting%20on%20the%20ground%20next%20to%20a%20tank%2C%20while%20others%20were%20led%20by%20a%20soldier%20to%20a%20gathering%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20and%20medical%20officials%20said%20Israeli%20forces%20were%20bombing%20houses%20and%20besieging%20hospitals%2C%20preventing%20medical%20and%20food%20supplies%20from%20entering%20to%20force%20them%20to%20leave%20the%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20officials%20said%20they%20refused%20orders%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army%20to%20evacuate%20the%20hospital%20or%20leave%20the%20patients%2C%20many%20in%20a%20critical%20condition%2C%20unattended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Israeli%20occupation%20is%20intensifying%20its%20targeting%20of%20the%20health%20system%20in%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20by%20besieging%20and%20directly%20targeting%20the%20Indonesian%20Hospital%2C%20Kamal%20Adwan%20Hospital%2C%20and%20Al-Awda%20Hospital%20during%20the%20past%20hours%20and%20its%20insistence%20on%20putting%20them%20out%20of%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20two%20patients%20in%20intensive%20care%20at%20the%20Indonesian%20Hospital%20died%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20result%20of%20the%20hospital's%20siege%20and%20the%20power%20outage%20and%20medical%20supplies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20the%20troops%20operating%20in%20the%20area%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bbriefed%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20mitigating%20harm%20to%20civilians%20and%20medical%20infrastructure%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20emphasized%20that%20the%20hospital%20continues%20to%20operate%20without%20disruption%20and%20in%20full%20capacity%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20intentional%20fire%20directed%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A172936134000