%20drinks%20have%20been%20an%20autumnal%20staple%20since%20the%20PSL%20was%20introduced%20in%202003%2C%20but%20multiple%20retailers%20are%20now%20offering%20wide%20selections%20of%20other%20fall-themed%20products.%20Depending%20on%20where%20you%20shop%2C%20you%20can%20find%20decor%2C%20candles%2C%20and%20samosas%20in%20fall%20flavors%20or%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20season%20used%20to%20be%20a%20relatively%20slow%20time%20for%20retailers%2C%20with%20no%20big%20sales%20to%20boost%20how%20much%20shoppers%20spent%20at%20stores.%20That%20has%20changed%20in%20recent%20times.%20Halloween%20sales%20have%20grown%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20National%20Retail%20Federation.%20Retailers%20have%20also%20added%20early%20holiday%20shopping%20events%2C%20such%20as%20Amazon's%20Prime%20Day%2C%20some%20of%20which%20started%20during%20the%20first%20week%20of%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20widely%2C%20fall-themed%20products%20represent%20another%20way%20for%20retailers%20and%20brands%20to%20fill%20out%20their%20sales%20schedule%2C%20according%20to%20Ronald%20Hill%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20marketing%20at%20American%20University's%20Kogod%20School%20of%20Business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20between%20what%20they%20can%20do%20in%20the%20summer%20and%20what%20they%20can%20do%20during%20the%20holidays%2C%26quot%3B%20Hill%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20gives%20you%20another%20twist%20around%20the%20calendar%20and%20a%20different%20season%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20people%20engaged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarget's%20fall%20selection%20this%20year%20includes%20about%20650%20new%20food%20items%2C%20including%20150%20from%20Target's%20store%20brands%2C%20Rick%20Gomez%2C%20the%20retailer's%20chief%20commercial%20officer%2C%20said%20on%20the%20company's%20earnings%20call%20in%20August.%20Products%20include%20Glazed%20Pumpkin%20Spice%20donut%20holes%20and%20sandwich%20cookies%20shaped%20like%20jack-o-lanterns%2C%20both%20sold%20under%20Target's%20Favorite%20Day%20brand.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20consumers%20are%20eager%20for%20their%20apple%20and%20pumpkin%20spice%20favorites%2C%26quot%3B%20Gomez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrader%20Joe's%20is%20offering%20148%20items%20with%20fall%20flavors%20or%20themes%2C%20from%20Mini%20Spicy%20Pumpkin%20Samosas%20to%20Pumpkin%20Body%20Scrub%2C%20according%20to%20the%20grocer's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.traderjoes.com%2Fhome%2Fdiscover%2Fstories%2Ffall-products-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20food.%20Lowe's%20is%20offering%20items%20including%20fall%20harvest%20decor%20and%20lawn%20inflatables%20for%20Halloween%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bbigger%20than%20ever%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20merchandising%20Bill%20Boltz%20said%20in%20August.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-depot-record-halloween-sales-giant-skeleton-sold-out-october-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHome%20Depot's%20massive%20skeleton%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20such%20a%20hit%20in%202020%20that%20it%20sold%20out%20before%20October%3B%20while%20its%20website%20shows%20the%20%24299%2012-foot%20Skelly%20is%20currently%20out%20of%20stock%2C%20customers%20can%20still%20buy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D6d2f70152f9cc21a36eb531c7671809ac77f9b817a8de7a2baf95a01f133f4f4%26postID%3D670fda5d0c43543ec7bcfebb%26postSlug%3Dfall-has-become-its-own-shopping-season-retail-2024-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.homedepot.com%252Fp%252FHome-Accents-Holiday-7-ft-Skelly-s-Dog-24SV24171%252F328196867%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%207-foot%20Skelly's%20Dog%20for%20%24199%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20Facebook%20page%20dedicated%20to%20discount%20grocer%20Aldi%2C%20shoppers%20posted%20pictures%20last%20month%20of%20themselves%20with%20