%2C%20especially%20residents%20of%20rural%20mountain%20towns%2C%20political%20analysts%20and%20candidates%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20expect%20turnout%20to%20be%20lower%20in%20the%20state's%20western%20region.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprojects.fivethirtyeight.com%2Fpolls%2Fpresident-general%2F2024%2Fnorth-carolina%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elatest%20polls%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eformer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20are%20neck-and-neck%2C%20and%20North%20Carolina%20remains%20a%20critical%20battleground%20state%20for%20either%20candidate's%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoting%20is%20not%20the%20top%20priority%20for%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20people%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chris%20Cooper%2C%20a%20political%20science%20professor%20at%20Western%20Carolina%20University.%20%26quot%3BEven%20among%20the%20most%20committed%20voters.%20If%20they%20don't%20have%20drinkable%20water%2C%20their%20priorities%20have%20shuffled.%20So%20I%20expect%20voter%20turnout%20to%20be%20down%20in%20the%20most-affected%20counties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECooper%20said%20his%20home%20was%20largely%20spared%20by%20Helene%2C%20but%20some%20family%20members%20who%20live%20in%20Asheville%20temporarily%20relocated%20to%20South%20Carolina.%20That%20includes%20his%20dad%2C%20who%20had%20planned%20to%20vote%20early%20and%20in-person%20but%20now%20must%20request%20a%20mail-in%20ballot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20voting%20began%20in%20North%20Carolina%20on%20October%2017%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncsbe.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F10%2F18%2Fnorth-carolina-sets-turnout-record-first-day-early-voting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estate%20election%20officials%20said%20in-person%20turnout%20topped%20a%20previous%20record%20set%20in%202020.%3C%2Fa%3E%20At%20the%20county%20level%2C%20state%20election%20officials%20told%20BI%20that%20comparing%20this%20year's%20numbers%20to%202020%20wouldn't%20be%20accurate%20due%20to%20several%20caveats%2C%20including%20that%20the%20absentee-by-mail%20voting%20period%20started%20two%20weeks%20earlier%20in%202020%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethan%20it%20did%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rural%20mountain%20areas%20of%20North%20Carolina%20previously%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efavored%20Trump.%20He%20won%20North%20Carolina%20by%20less%20than%2075%2C000%20votes%20in%20the%202020%20presidential%20race%2C%20with%20strong%20support%20in%20areas%20outside%20urban%20centers.%20That%20included%2011%20of%20the%2013%20counties%20hardest-hit%20by%20Helene.%20The%20two%20exceptions%20were%20Buncombe%20County%2C%20where%20Asheville%20is%20located%2C%20and%20Watauga%20County.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stands%20near%20a%20home%20with%20a%20Trump%202024%20campaign%20sign%20as%20he%20coordinates%20relief%20in%20Lake%20Lure%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20on%20October%202%2C%202024%20after%20Hurricane%20Helene.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712c0f5a0a0cc14f2225dd6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20man%20coordinates%20relief%20in%20Lake%20Lure%2C%20North%20Carolina%20after%20Hurricane%20Helene.%3Cp%3EAllison%20Joyce%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Democrats%20aim%20to%20flip%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Felection%2F2020%2Fresults%2Fstate%2Fnorth-carolina%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistorically%20red%3C%2Fa%3E%20North%20Carolina%2C%20seeing%20a%20path%20in%20the%20rapidly%20growing%20suburban%20areas%20like%20Charlotte%2C%20Raleigh-Durham%2C%20and%20Fayetteville.%20Harris%20is%20trying%20to%20win%20over%20Black%20and%20college%20educated%20voters%2C%20as%20well%20as%20women%20who%20oppose%20the%20state's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plannedparenthood.org%2Fplanned-parenthood-south-atlantic%2Fpatients%2Fhealth-care-services%2Fabortion-services%2Fnc-abortion-faqs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestrictive%20abortion%20law%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Helene%20has%20become%20a%20political%20lightning%20rod%2C%20with%20Trump%20attacking%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6b2ed09-6d41-465a-9740-c901aa87fc11%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOfficials%20say%20North%20Carolinians%20know%20the%20importance%20of%20voting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20ways%20to%20reach%20people%2C%20such%20as%20door%20knocking%20and%20social%20media%2C%20aren't%20as%20accessible%20because%20of%20the%20destruction%20and%20spotty%20internet%20service.%20This%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20campaign%20staff%20to%20canvas%20and%20combat%20rumors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20spread%20disinformation%2C%20telling%20attendees%20at%20a%20campaign%20rally%20that%20Harris%20stole%20Federal%20Emergency%20Management%20Agency%20(FEMA)%20disaster%20relief%20funding%20and%20spent%20it%20on%20housing%20for%20migrants.%20He%20also%20wrote%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F113227266617485932%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETruth%20Social%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20Gov.%20Roy%20Cooper%2C%20a%20Democrat%2C%20were%20going%20out%20of%20their%20way%20to%20not%20assist%20Republican-leaning%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20and%20some%20GOP%20politicians%20have%20debunked%20the%20claims%2C%20including%20Rep.%20Chuck%20Edwards%2C%20a%20Republican%20who%20represents%20North%20Carolina's%2011th%20district%2C%20which%20was%20devastated%20by%20Helene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdwards%20told%20BI%20that%20he's%20been%20working%20around%20the%20clock%20to%20connect%20survivors%20with%20the%20resources%20they%20need.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedwards.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Fdebunking-helene-response-myths%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20statement%20on%20October%208%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20being%20inundated%20with%20emails%20and%20calls%20from%20people%20upset%20about%20unfounded%20rumors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20getting%20calls%20from%20people%20around%20the%20country%20who%20wanted%20to%20send%20personnel%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%20water%2C%20but%20worried%20it%20wouldn't%20make%20it%20to%20the%20right%20location%20because%20of%20the%20rumors%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwards%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BPrimarily%2C%20that%20FEMA%20was%20confiscating%20supplies%20and%20turning%20people%20away.%20There%20is%20absolutely%20no%20truth%20to%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdwards%20added%20that%20even%20though%20folks%20are%20busy%20putting%20their%20lives%20back%20together%2C%20they%20understand%20that%20an%20important%20election%20is%20right%20around%20the%20corner.%20They%20are%20motivated%20to%20get%20out%20and%20vote%20for%20Trump%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20remember%20what%20our%20lives%20were%20like%20the%20day%20before%20the%20storm%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwards%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20inflation%2C%20oil%20prices%2C%20and%20a%20crisis%20at%20the%20Southern%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdwards'%20competitor%2C%20Rep.%20Caleb%20Rudow%2C%20is%20a%20Democrat%20who%20represents%20Buncombe%20county%20in%20the%20state%20legislature.%20He's%20been%20canvassing%20and%20posting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FCalebRudow%2Fstatus%2F1846144971256057972%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20talking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20this%20election%2C%20particularly%20after%20Helene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERudow%20said%20the%20state%20needs%20elected%20officials%20who%20want%20to%20solve%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20which%20is%20fueling%20more%20intense%20hurricanes.%20He%20also%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20relief%20work%20by%20state%2C%20local%2C%20and%20federal%