0better%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BThe%20European%20Kid%2C%26quot%3B%20at%20some%20point%20on%20your%20social%20media%20feeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeager%20has%20built%20a%20sizable%20online%20presence%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20%E2%80%94%20accumulating%201.7%20million%20followers%20on%20TikTok%20and%20one%20million%20on%20Instagram%20%E2%80%94%20by%20making%20videos%20that%20parody%20a%20sort%20of%20spoiled%20rich%20European%20caricature%20through%20a%20French-accented%20persona%20named%20Louis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20know%20who%20you're%20messing%20with!%26quot%3B%20Louis%20shouts%20in%20one%20video%2C%20trying%20to%20persuade%20well-known%20New%20York%20City%20bouncer%20Fabrizio%20Brienza%20to%20let%20him%20into%20a%20club.%20%26quot%3BThe%20richest%20family%20in%20Europe!%20Do%20you%20know%20who%20my%20dad%20is%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20which%20has%20over%2045%20million%20views%20on%20TikTok%2C%20is%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20just%20how%20bizarre%20Yeager's%20life%20has%20become%20in%20a%20short%20time%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20viewers%20did%20not%20pick%20up%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20videos%20are%20satire%2C%20so%20some%20assumed%20he%20was%20the%20son%20of%20Bernard%20Arnault%2C%20the%20richest%20man%20in%20Europe%20who%20founded%20LVMH%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20Louis%20Vuitton%2C%20Dior%2C%20Mo%C3%ABt%20%26amp%3B%20Chandon%2C%20and%20other%20luxury%20brands.%20Major%20French%20television%20station%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tf1info.fr%2Fsociete%2Ftu-sais-qui-je-suis-le-fils-de-bernard-arnault-filme-en-train-de-se-mettre-en-colere-contre-un-videur-2274596.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETF1%20wrote%20a%20story%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0about%20the%20mix-up%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Falexarnault%2Fstatus%2F1718665404384444593%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlexandre%20Arnault%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20real%20son%20of%20Bernard%20Arnault%2C%20had%20to%20clarify%20that%20it%20was%20not%20him%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20you%20looked%20up%20Bernard%20Arnault%20on%20Google%2C%20my%20video%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20videos%20that%20popped%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Yeager%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20that%20is%20one%20of%20the%20craziest%20moments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20conflation%20between%20Yeager's%20and%20Louis'%20life%20goes%20further%20than%20being%20mistaken%20for%20billionaires'%20sons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20videos%20are%20a%20parody%2C%20Yeager%20is%20still%20personally%20in%20places%20like%20Saint-Tropez%2C%20St.%20Moritz%2C%20and%20the%20Hamptons%2C%20after%20all.%20Because%20of%20his%20newfound%20fame%2C%20he's%20mingled%20with%20celebrities%20like%20Formula%201%20driver%20Carlos%20Sainz%20Jr.%2C%20actor%20Anne%20Hathaway%2C%20and%20snowboarder%20Shaun%20White.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20be%20a%20Formula%201%20driver%2C%26quot%3B%20Louis%20told%20Sainz%20in%20a%20video%20earlier%20this%20year.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20saying%20I'm%20going%20to%20beat%20you%2C%20but%20I%20think%20I%20will.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeager%20said%20that%20brand%20sponsorships%20have%20allowed%20him%20to%20generate%20an%20income%20somewhere%20in%20the%20six-figure%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20his%20life%20isn't%20exactly%20like%20Louis'%20might%20appear.%20Yeager%20said%20many%20of%20his%20videos%20shot%20in%20seaside%20villas%2C%20private%20jets%2C%20boats%2C%20and%20luxury%20city%20apartments%20are%20actually%20offered%20up%20by%20real-estate%20agents%20looking%20to%20promote%20a%20property%2C%20jet%20and%20boat%20companies%20looking%20to%20advertise%2C%20or%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20on%20social%20media%20is%20exaggerated%2C%26quot%3B%20Yeager%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20always%20take%20it%20with%20a%20grain%20of%20salt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20on%20trips%20to%20exotic%20places%2C%20he%20usually%20stays%20only%20a%20few%20days%20and%20is%20primarily%20there%20to%20shoot%20several%20videos%20for%20his%20channel%20before%20returning%20to%20New%20York%2C%20where%20he's%20lived%20since%20graduating%20from%20Northeastern%20University%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20Yeager%20is%20busy%20building%20a%20business%20that%20seeks%20to%20pair%20influencers%20like%20himself%20with%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20ironically%2C%20given%20his%20big-brand%2C%20rich-kid%20persona%20%E2%80%94%20small%20businesses%20looking%20for%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20is%20an%20app%20that%20launched%20in%20April%20called%20Storytime.%20Yeager%20founded%20it%20with%20Philip%20Davis%2C%20his%20former%20colleague%20at%20Lefty%2C%20another%20influencer-focused%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Storytime%20has%20financial%20backing%20from%20Lefty%20founder%20Thomas%20Repelski%2C%20as%20well%20as%20around%20%24150%2C000%20from%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20Davis%20and%20Yeager%20said.%20It%20has%201%2C000%20influencer%20users%20that%20they%20individually%20vet%2C%20they%20said%2C%20and%20over%20a%20hundred%20businesses%20that%20pay%20a%20%24100-a-month%20subscription%20fee%20for%20access%20to%20the%20pool%20of%20influencers.%20The%20businesses%20can%20automate%20offers%20for%20free%20products%20in%20exchange%20for%20posts%20from%20influencers%20with%20localized%2C%20targeted%20audiences%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20larger%20follower%20counts%20that%20may%20be%20irrelevant%20to%20a%20particular%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20client%20of%20Yeager%20and%20Davis%20is%20Milano%20Market%20on%20Manhattan's%20Upper%20East%20Side.%20The%20duo%20recently%20filmed%20a%20video%20with%20its%20owner%2C%20where%20Louis%20attempts%20to%20buy%20an%20entire%20%242%2C000%20wheel%20of%20parmesan%20cheese%2C%20only%20to%20be%20stopped%20by%20the%20owner%20who%20is%20concerned%20about%20Louis'%20intentions%20wit