%2527s%2520Cofounder%2520and%2520CEO%2520%252D%2520Business%2520Insider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20is%20always%20in%20the%20media%20spotlight%2C%20fielding%20many%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFVRHTWWEIz4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20which%20was%20just%20made%20public%2C%20venture%20capitalist%20Patrick%20Chung%20passed%20the%20proverbial%20mic%20back%20to%20Altman%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20share%20the%20one%20question%20he'd%20most%20like%20to%20be%20asked%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-explained-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20general%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20its%20inception%20in%202015%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-implosion-investors-vcs-2024-9%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOpenAI%2520is%2520at%2520the%2520forefront%2Cits%2520annualized%2520revenue%2520last%2520summer.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20aimed%20to%20achieve%20this%20still%20hypothetical%20form%20of%20robot%20intelligence%20that%20mimics%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eor%20even%20surpasses%20%E2%80%94%20human%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20offered%20two%20questions%3A%20What%20do%20you%20hope%20society%20looks%20like%20when%20AGI%20gets%20built%20and%20how%20do%20you%20conceptualize%20the%20positive%20version%20of%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20said%20his%20answer%20to%20these%20questions%20has%20evolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20original%20conception%20was%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20we%20like%2C%20get%20over%20the%20threshold%20to%20this%20self-improving%20superintelligence%2C%20and%20it's%20this%20magic%20thing%20in%20the%20tower%20that%20we%20can%20ask%20any%20question%2C%20and%20it%20answers%20it%2C%20and%20it's%20like%20constantly%20off%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20improve%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20It%20would%20be%2C%20at%20once%2C%20%26quot%3Butopic%20and%20extremely%20dystopic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20though%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20interview%20in%20May%20%E2%80%94%20Altman%20said%20we're%20headed%20to%20a%20world%20where%20AGI%20just%20%26quot%3Bsort%20of%20participates%20in%20society%20and%20in%20the%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20most%20part%2C%20it%20will%20manifest%20in%20tools%20that%20make%20individuals%20more%20productive%2C%20he%20said.%20However%2C%20it'll%20also%20facilitate%20the%20development%20of%20a%20body%20of%20%26quot%3Bshared%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20illustrating%20it%20with%20the%20metaphor%20of%20%26quot%3Bscaffolding%20that%20exists%20between%20all%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20one%20expert%20might%20contribute%20insight%20about%20material%20science%20to%20existing%20knowledge%20on%20the%20topic%2C%20which%20may%20help%20another%20group%20develop%20a%20transistor%20or%20a%20mini%20semiconductor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bsuperintelligence%20is%20not%20what%20exists%20in%20any%20one%20neural%20network.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20it%20emerges%20%26quot%3Bin%20this%20scaffolding%20between%20the%20neural%20networks%26quot%3B%20and%20forms%20a%20%26quot%3Btechnology%20tree%26quot%3B%20that%20enables%20society%20to%20achieve%20goals%20beyond%20the%20capabilities%20of%20any%20individual%20neural%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20more%20recently%20said%20that%20his%20experience%20at%20Burning%20Man%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Business%20Insider's%20Rob%20Price%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-escaped-burning-man-mud-apocalypse-climate-change-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bannual%20campout-slash-rave-slash-art-exhibition-slash-ephemeral-city%20that%20blooms%20and%20disappears%20in%20the%20Black%20Rock%20Desert%20%E2%80%94%20helped%20him%20better%20envision%20this%20new%20frontier.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt%20showed%20him%20one%20part%20of%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20the%20post-AGI%20world%20can%20look%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-loves-burning-man-agi-world-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAltman%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Life%20in%20Seven%20Songs%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20people%20are%20just%20focused%20on%20doing%20stuff%20for%20each%20other%2C%20caring%20for%20each%20other%2C%20and%20making%20incredible%20gifts%20to%20give%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ceo-sam-altman-favorite-question-about-agi-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729344311000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67129ccafd8ede6c99e4052e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ceo-sam-altman-favorite-question-about-agi-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Altman%20said%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20will%20facilitate%20%26quot%3Bscaffolding%20that%20exists%20between%20all%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40insider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ceo-sam-altman-favorite-question-about-agi-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Firebombs%20thrown%20at%20Japan's%20ruling%20party%20HQ%20and%20car%20rammed%20into%20security%20fence%20around%20PM's%20office%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729343820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F10%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-japan-tokyo_6720517.jpg%3F20241019114955%22%2C%